<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>All of the Curscale Armor is great for Starting Iksar Monks and can be gotten by a Merchant directly in front of the Monk Guild.  Master Glok is facing the building where the merchant is.  Just "Hail" the merchant and he gives the quest.  The merchant also sells armor there, but it is not as good as the Curscale.  The quest also give decent exp for newbies.</font></td></tr></table>
